Package: ALTRE
Type: Package
Title: Workflow: Post-alignment to altered enhancers
    and promoters
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Elizabeth Baskin, Rick Farouni, Ewy Mathe
Maintainer: Elizabeth Baskin <Elizabeth.Baskin@osumc.edu>, Ewy Mathe <Ewy.Mathe@osumc.edu>
Description: This workflow takes alignment data and hotspot calls from
    assays of open chromatin (ATAC-seq, Dnase-seq, and FAIRE-seq) and identifies
    regions (enhancers and promoters) that differ based on cell and
    tissue type.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    shiny,
    shinydashboard,
    rmarkdown,
    methods,
    S4Vectors,
    GenomeInfoDb,
    IRanges,
    DESeq2,
    GenomicAlignments,
    SummarizedExperiment,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2,
    GenomicRanges,
    Rsamtools,
    readr,
    org.Hs.eg.db,
    clusterProfiler,
    ensembldb,
    EnsDb.Hsapiens.v75
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
NeedsCompilation: no
